Spatial Analysis
To refine the urban classification, we identify OAs that fall within major towns or cities. These areas are reclassified as “Urban: within major town or city” to distinguish them from other urban or rural locations.


Show the code
id_town &lt;- st_within(oa_boundaries, towns_boundaries)

oa_boundaries$id_town &lt;- vapply(
  id_town,
  \(x) {
    if (length(x) == 1) {
      x
    } else {
      NA_integer_
    }
  },
  numeric(1)
)

Downloading Sub-ICB (Clinical Commissioning Group) boundary data from OpenPrescribing.


