Identifying GP practices located within CAZ buffer zones.


Show the code
caz_practices &lt;- all_practices[caz_buffers, ]


Classifying practices by their distance from CAZ boundaries and assigning CAZ names.


Show the code
practices_intersects &lt;- st_intersects(caz_practices, caz_buffers)

caz_practices$buffer_km &lt;- vapply(
  practices_intersects,
  \(caz_index) {
    caz_buffers$buffer_km[caz_index] |&gt; min()
  },
  FUN.VALUE = numeric(1)
)

caz_practices$CAZ_name &lt;- vapply(
  practices_intersects,
  \(caz_index) {
    caz_buffers$name[caz_index][which.min(caz_buffers$buffer_km[caz_index])]
  },
  FUN.VALUE = character(1)
)




